title: Oliver's Real Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Quick service organic fast food eatery with outlets in NSW and VIC. Uses natural ingredients. Its webpage lists separate menus for vegetarian, vegan, dairy-free, and gluten-free choices. This outlet is located in the Shell Service Centre with also grab-n-go selection.
